               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MESSRS. POLATD</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">and</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MEAD</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">conducted the Prosecution; and</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. STRAIGHT</hi>. <hi rend="italic">the Defence.</hi>
